      "effect": "You can use this Skill's first and second effects if your Extra Deck contains 2 or more Level 8 or lower Fusion Monsters.\n1: At the beginning of the Duel, gain 1600 LP.\n2: During the End Phase of a turn you Special Summoned a Level 8 or lower Fusion Monster, gain 400 LP."
